title: GabaTrendtin 9/15: Miles' Special Day, Big Trouble, Dumped, Roger Federer, CNN, 'The Woman King'
itunes:title: GabaTrendtin 9/15: Miles' Special Day, Big Trouble, Dumped, Roger Federer, CNN, 'The Woman King'
description:
In this edition of GabaTrendtin, Jack and Miles discuss Miles' special day, "big trouble" in Mar-A-Lago, the Right dumping migrants all over the country, Roger Federer announcing his retirement, Don Lemon getting demoted to mornings at CNN, and the new film 'The Woman King'!
